snippet.title: D | D no Shokutaku - Live! 3DO Magazine Trailer 2
snippet.description:
As seen on the fifth issue of Live! 3DO Magazine from Japan, this is one of the previews for D, a cult classic adventure game from the late Kenji Eno.

Developed by WARP
Published in Japan by Sanyei Shobou
D: The Game, D no Shokutaku (C) Throwback Entertainment
Also released on SEGA Saturn, MS-DOS and PlayStation
